name: Feeling a Little Sheepy
description:
In the summer of 2021 I decided to try my hand at painting with acrylics on canvas.  This is one of the artworks I created.  

It has hung it in my bedroom since then and is one of the first things I see each day, it always makes me smile, so I hope it finds collectors that get he same feeling.  

This painting was inspired by a trip I took to Ireland with my son in 2018.
